==评价==
根据[[NPD集团|NPD集团]]的数据，2009年9月期间，任天堂DS版《涂鸦冒险家》在美国卖出了19万4千份，仅次于同平台的《[[瑪利歐與路易吉RPG3!!!|瑪利歐與路易吉RPG3!!!]]》和《[[王國之心_358/2天|王國之心 358/2天]]》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/10/20/scribblenauts-sees-solid-september-sales | title = Scribblenauts Sees Solid September Sales | first = Ryan | last = Geddes | website = IGN | date = 2009-10-19 | access-date = 2009-10-19 | archive-date = 2020-07-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200714165141/https://www.ign.com/articles/2009/10/20/scribblenauts-sees-solid-september-sales | dead-url = no }}</ref>。该游戏在2009年12月仍然销售强劲，是该月北美地区最畅销游戏第16名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26832/NPD_Wii_DS_Titles_Command_December_2009_Top_20.php | title = NPD: Wii, DS Titles Command December 2009 Top 20 | first = Kris | last = Graft | date = 2010-01-15 | access-date = 2010-01-16 | website = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-date = 2019-01-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190111120845/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26832/NPD_Wii_DS_Titles_Command_December_2009_Top_20.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>。到2010年2月，该游戏已经在全球卖出了一百万套<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100203005463/en/Warner-Bros.-Interactive-Entertainment-Announces-Scribblenauts%E2%84%A2-Sells | title = Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment Announces Scribblenauts Sells In More Than One Million Units Worldwide | publisher = [[美國商業資訊|美國商業資訊]] | date = 2010-02-03 | access-date = 2015-01-25 | archive-date = 2020-12-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201212151705/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100203005463/en/Warner-Bros.-Interactive-Entertainment-Announces-Scribblenauts%E2%84%A2-Sells | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》将《涂鸦冒险家》评为2009年度第七佳电子游戏<ref>{{cite news | url = http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1945379_1944169_1944185,00.html | title = The Top 10 Everything of 2009 | first = Lev | last = Grossman | author2 = Ha, Peter | date = 2009-12-08 | access-date = 2009-12-10 | work = [[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]] | archive-date = 2020-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200112083237/http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1945379_1944169_1944185,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

